she'd wake up foggy, confused, and feeling worse than before. She tried melatonin. Gummies. Teas. Magnesium. Nothing gave her real sleep.<br><br>So <span style="color: inherit">RC</span>, a student at the University of Pennsylvania, started researching why everything on the market either didn't work or came with brutal side effects. What he found changed everything: the problem wasn't the ingredients — it was how the body absorbed them. That insight is what led to the development of Rejuvia's Oral Sleep Spray. His mom was the first customer and she finally could sleep through the night. Today, over 300,000 people do too.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="e41a81bd-52c8-4f8a-9eb7-67f37add7ce0" class="r-1hcdcng"><div data-rid="9a702686-836e-45ca-b05c-859b3ade5616" class="r-1nqjdb1"><picture data-rid="874f685c-fde3-41dd-aeb4-a6166167a6bd" class="r-i9ijx0"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/edd42447-2fbd-468b-bb89-ddd67ae5cc9b?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/edd42447-2fbd-468b-bb89-ddd67ae5cc9b?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/edd42447-2fbd-468b-bb89-ddd67ae5cc9b?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/edd42447-2fbd-468b-bb89-ddd67ae5cc9b" alt="A hand holding a purple Rejuvia spray against a clear blue sky." class="r-18gwgsw" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="cdbe5ce9-0734-4ac6-9b26-43ca6b232fbb" class="r-17m0rjj"><div data-rid="d8e286b9-d8ef-4311-901e-aabd5e15ed8c" class="r-1pe03ij"><div data-rid="a708525b-7d66-419c-8fa2-8fa42e31dc42" class="r-y6k4p9"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="presentation" style="width: