9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><p>Helps You Fall Asleep 3x Faster Each Night</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="310add15-614d-44bd-ba5b-4b405f4901af" class="r-ilbsjv"><div data-rid="579e269b-da22-42c3-8753-8d1ab870f287" class="r-1hf3vbt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Here's the problem with every pill and gummy on the market: they have to survive your stomach. Your digestive system breaks them down over 60-90 minutes, destroying most of the active ingredients before they ever reach your bloodstream. You're swallowing a full dose but your body only absorbs a fraction of it.<br><br>Rejuvia skips that entire process. You spray it under your tongue, where it absorbs directly into your bloodstream in minutes — no digestion, no waiting, no wasted ingredients. Your body absorbs up to 60% more of the active sleep compounds compared to pills. That's why most customers are asleep within 10-15 minutes of their nightly sprays.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="795859df-fb5d-4c10-9d12-5e147d832202" class="r-pf7vdo"><div data-rid="673a504e-0f56-4ac6-b9d1-fca06a3fa210" class="r-p8a9d2"><picture data-rid="c51e4763-204a-4245-b66d-611c9707098c" class="r-1w94au2"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/dffe8fc2-c9ed-4803-adfe-1992dfcf515f?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/dffe8fc2-c9ed-4803-adfe-1992dfcf515f?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/dffe8fc2-c9ed-4803-adfe-1992dfcf515f?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/dffe8fc