00;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1></span></div><div data-rid="6f17cdde-208f-4a72-893c-6a6b48ca30c9" class="r-1cdt99m" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="f738d2a8-5d3d-4234-9e59-7c15e6fd79b1" class="r-iln6jo" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="6683a1a0-9652-429d-b227-08bdee594689" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R3br2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-j9ngmg"><div data-rid="dd8ea80a-6f67-45d0-97c2-0d57b1d2b71a" class="r-taatj0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What are the ingredients in Rejuvia?</p></span></div><div data-rid="53c20bd0-9c0d-4684-87c0-53f321a0de94" class="r-m3ujpp" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-uenq8p" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R3br2:"><div data-rid="16e365ea-8133-454e-a9f4-699dd867b55d" class="r-105goqn"><div data-rid="9d1f3c00-e625-4039-b3f0-b44ef728b6ce" class="r-k4v6a4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Rejuvia’s Sleep Spray is made with a clean blend of natural, science-backed ingredients that help you fall asleep faster, stay asleep longer, and wake up clear. Each serving includes melatonin to support your body’s natural sleep cycle, 5-HTP to promote relaxation and mood balance, and a proprietary blend of calming herbs like passionflower, valerian, lemon balm, chamomile, hops, and magnolia bark. These ingredients work together to calm your nervous system, lower stress, and support deep, restorative sleep. Rejuvia is non-habit forming, gentle on your body, and made with natural peppermint flavor and clean ingredients.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="ca3fbbb7-5df2-4c90-8dab-54f3c815c49c" class="r-kf8ut0" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="657d4fd6-7480-442a-b7c0-42acbfa7a81a" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R5br2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1a14v7a"><div data-rid="c4d6f8e2-f56d-489b-8264-0666383120a4" class="r-dsmlxo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How long does one spray last?</p></span></div><div data-rid="25edc735-70aa-4f29-bf27-0dd7190d46ae" class="r-1r63syb" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1v3i5yz" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R5br2:"><div data-rid="20d9c59c-4ab9-48d3-9318-3188ffa3bc27" class="r-lpr1m1"><div data-rid="eacd9240-415a-4982-b8c7-e1f109da2f64" class="r-safo6d alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>One bottle of Rejuvia typically lasts about 30 nights when used as directed. Most people use 6 to 8 sprays before bed, which delivers the ideal amount for fast, deep, and consistent sleep. Because the spray absorbs so efficiently through your mouth, you don’t need large doses to feel the effects. It’s designed to fit seamlessly into your nightly routine — quick, simple, and long-lasting.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="fff82a2e-297d-472f-8a41-0f438de46a6f" class="r-19h5ywc" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" da