div><div data-rid="390d6567-6ed8-4d4b-bbf6-0381ef8bfaf0" class="r-18jeunh" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1mw2o4w" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R9br2:"><div data-rid="f604e3ac-fa16-42de-91aa-255b16ffcf7b" class="r-gq2t8s"><div data-rid="3bae517c-6344-492c-9951-248390d4ad51" class="r-usaidv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes. The sprays are non-habit forming, all-natural, and safe for nightly use. There’s no dependency or “getting used to it” — just consistent, restorative sleep over time.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="ea9133d3-c5d1-4123-a866-7c563642f45d" class="r-x4i8ym" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="2da9ffd9-5941-4594-ba72-bbaa464757ca" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rbbr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1ds2vlw"><div data-rid="4d2204f1-6eaa-4df0-b7a3-8aec120e00a7" class="r-xc96vu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Does Rejuvia have side effects?</p></span></div><div data-rid="908fb036-0321-4ce3-b59c-aedbce4542bc" class="r-hgav8n" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-7vmnwz" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rbbr2:"><div data-rid="38125a45-6b01-4387-9482-46dd74ffe3c1" class="r-4y2kbg